    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>Enter your password into the <em>TextBox </em>and press 'Check' button to ckeck it.<br />The information about password strength will be displayed below.<br />Press 'Help' button to show window with help information about password strength levels.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>UserControl </em>control is functionally equivalent to the Windows Forms <em>UserControl </em>control and can be used on the <em>Form </em>in similar way.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
